data.description: Welcome to the heart of Millwood, where your ideal home awaits! This open-concept ranch-style gem is nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac, featuring a fenced backyard for added privacy. With a double-car garage, 3 bedrooms, and 2 baths, this residence is designed for both comfort and style. The en-suite master bedroom comes complete with a walk-in closet, providing a luxurious retreat within your own home. Vaulted ceilings add an airy and spacious feel, complemented by modern amenities such as a sprinkler system, gas forced air heat, and central air conditioning, kitchen new appliances and a brand new gas hot water tank.  Convenience is key, with shopping and schools in close proximity. Embrace the perfect blend of contemporary living and a coveted location in this Millwood haven. Your dream home is here – seize the opportunity!
